{"tid":556190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街鄭泳舜打壓社區服務,阻人過年","createTime":"2018-02-10T09:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T11:55:22.000Z","uid":131064,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebfe130008f925c48d9f88f1badc5822371fddb","tid":556190,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/174807_bcc90e98e586a979a9ca329088a66934.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F174807_bcc90e98e586a979a9ca329088a66934.png&h=7b5e75e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">未當選就當自己特權階級</span></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n小編路過黃埔站，見到民建聯候選人鄭泳舜竟然同區內民主派一同宣傳？！<br />\n<br />\n細問鄺議員同 紅土家朋友先發現原來民建聯刻意用宣傳品霸住佢哋舉行活動地點，阻撓佢哋下晝2點開始嘅寫揮春活動，而鄺議員亦都同民建聯義工交涉，但小編見到佢哋態度明顯為阻礙人哋舉行活動為目的，令到小編都好憤怒，人家為社區做事，為何要惡意阻撓？<br />\n<br />\n各位居民，我哋社區要這樣的候選人嗎？<br />\n<br />\n*九西補選候選人另有姚松炎和蔡東洲"},{"pid":"1f950245f98fdcc303c1c28fb07c67d098a62e14","tid":556190,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb2c50d7ecdc768380651d04ae7ef898ab5252c","tid":556190,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"喂，偷我Topic😡😡😡😡<br />\n殺死你"},{"pid":"25515e2616b80b7109c750ee22c2cc4d60ee8135","tid":556190,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:55:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}